 in trouble! } 9. Nxc3 $16 { [%cal Gc1g5,Gc3d5,Gf1e1,Gb5e8][%csl Gc3,Rc6,Re7]With ideas such as Nd5 and Bg5, our forces are simply overwhelming Black. Their King is still crying for help. } * 

