lack's pieces are not so close. Black now again has only one move to fight for equality which is After } 18... Nc8 $146 { , not an easy move to find at all! If Black takes } ( 18... hxg4 { , we recapture with the Queen } 19. Qxg4 { , still ready to play h5 next. } ) ( 18... Nc8 $146 { , we can continue with } 19. Qd4 { , forcing Black to play } 19... f6 { after which we can consider either } 20. Rfe1 { or first taking } ( 20. gxh5 { , in both cases with the initiative. } ) ) * 

