..Be7 (See the corresponding variation from the PGN). } ) 9. h3 Ne3 $1 { [%cal Ge6c4][%csl Rc4,Re3]A very sleek tactic! After } ( 9... Nf6 $2 $146 10. Ng5 $40 $146 { The e6-Bishop is under immense pressure. After } 10... Nd8 $146 { White can increase the pressure with } 11. Qf3 { . } ) 10. fxe3 { [%cal Ge1e8,Ge3d4,Ge6c4][%csl Rc4,Re8]} 10... Bxc4 11. exd4+ { [%cal Ge1e8][%csl Gd4,Ge1,Re8]Catching Black's King in the center. } 11... Be7 12. Be3 { [%cal Gb1d2][%csl Rc4]With Nbd2 to come next, White has a very stable center and grip on the position. The Black Knight on c6 is misplaced, just staring at the d4-pawn. } * 

