King in the center. } ) 12... Qg5 { [%cal Gg5e5,Gg5g2,Ga6f1][%csl Re1,Re5,Rg2]Black tries to catch the White King. However, we now have a very strong reply. } 13. Qd4 $18 { [%cal Gg5g2,Ge1c1,Gc5e6,Gd4e3,Ge3g5][%csl Rc5,Gd4,Rg5]A key move! Now if Black takes } 13... Qxg2 { we can castle long, } 14. O-O-O { , and if Black plays 13. Qd4 13...Ne6 we offer a Queen trade with 14.Qe3 . } * 

