16... Rcd2 $4 { Black's Rooks on the d-file look strong... But there is a hidden weakness! Can you find it? } 17. Nd5 $1 { [%cal Gd1d2][%csl Rd2][%cal Gd5e7][%csl Re7]Disturbing the connection between Black's Rooks! } 17... Qg5 18. Rxd2 { White trades Rooks with a strong idea in mind! } 18... Qxd2 19. Rd1 { [%cal Gd1d8][%csl Rd8,Rd2,Gd1]Now the d8-Rook is exposed to a discovered check. Black loses material! } 19... Qg5 20. Nf6+ { [%cal Gd1d8][%csl Rd8][%cal Rg5d8][%csl Rg8,Gf6]POW! The final blow, the game is over! } * 

